OL,3,CDriver charged after taxi passenger
OL,4,Cdies in crash
OL,6,FA man has been charged with multiple
OL,7,Foffences after a taxi passenger was
OL,8,Fkilled in a car crash.
OL,10,FLancashire Police was called to
OL,11,FWestgate in Morecambe just after
OL,12,F5.45am on 10 August, after reports of
OL,13,Fa collision between a Ford Mondeo taxi
OL,14,Fand Fiat Punto.
OL,16,FThe rear seat passenger - a man in his
OL,17,F50s - died from his injuries, police
OL,18,Fsay.
