OL,3,CDriver charged after taxi passenger
OL,4,Cdies in crash
OL,6,FJez Shepherd, 22, has been charged
OL,7,Fwith causing death by dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving, driving whilst disqualified
OL,9,Fand driving with no insurance.
OL,11,FHe has also been charged with taking
OL,12,Fwithout consent causing death,
OL,13,Fburglary, making off without payment.
OL,15,FThe driver of the taxi, a 31-year-old
OL,16,Fman from Morecambe, arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,18,Fdangerous driving has been released on
OL,19,Fbail pending further enquiries.
