OL,6,FSergeant Martin Wilcock, a Senior
OL,7,FInvestigating Officer in the Road
OL,8,FPolicing Unit, said: "As a result of
OL,9,Fthis collision a man has lost his life
OL,10,Fand my thoughts very much remain with
OL,11,Fhis loved ones. They continue to be
OL,12,Fsupported by specially trained
OL,13,Fofficers at this extremely difficult
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,16,F"While a man has now been charged, I
OL,17,Fwant to make it clear that our
OL,18,Fenquiries are very much ongoing.
