OL,6,F"With that in mind I would ask any
OL,7,Fwitnesses or anyone with dashcam,
OL,8,Fmobile phone or CCTV footage that
OL,9,Fcould assist us in our investigation
OL,10,Fto make contact as soon as possible."
OL,12,FThose with information are asked to
OL,13,Fcontact 101 or email the force quoting
OL,14,Flog 270 of 10 August 2025.
